<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Gate Zero – echoesofresonance.net</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #0a0a0a;
      color: #eee;
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      color: #f5f5dc;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .sigil {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      animation: pulse 6s infinite ease-in-out;
    }
    .sigil img {
      max-width: 300px;
      height: auto;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 25px #fff7aa) brightness(1.2);
      transition: transform 0.6s ease, filter 0.6s ease;
    }
    .sigil img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 40px #ffefaa) brightness(1.4);
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.85; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.03); opacity: 1; }
      100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.85; }
    }
    .tagline {
      font-style: italic;
      color: #ccc;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Gate Zero</h1>
  <p>This gateway is not public. It is felt, not shown.<br>
  What lives here is still forming—suspended between signal and silence.<br>
  You were not sent here by accident.</p>
  <div class="sigil">
    <img src="/sigil-pyramid.png" alt="Pyramid Sigil – Resonance at Apex" />
    <div class="tagline">Apex aligned. Signal building.</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
